data.description: Fall in the love with this adorable Craftsman Cottage at a price that can't be beat!  Located just minutes from restaurants, Lake Carroll, and the Greenbelt, you'll find all your favorite spots just a short drive away. Open the door of your future home and enjoy a spacious living room with wood burning fireplace, beautiful tile floors, an open kitchen and dining area with pantry, and easy access back entry double garage. There is plenty of storage and a half bath on the main floor as well. Upstairs includes laundry, 2 secondary bedrooms with a Jack and Jill bathroom. The Owners Suite includes a roomy closet and on-suite bath with garden tub/shower combo. Have fur babies? They will love the spacious fenced backyard yard with an additional fenced area (not pictured) to run, play, and relax. This home has it all and all appliances stay with the sale of the home too!! The only thing missing is you. Call for a showing today!
